perl-IP-Country-DB_File: perl-IP-Country-DB_File (IPv4 and IPv6 to country translation)
perl-IP-Country-DB_File:
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: IP::Country::DB_File is a light-weight module for fast IP address to
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: country translation based on DB_File. The country code database is
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: stored in a Berkeley DB file. You have to build the database using
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: build_ipcc.pl or IP::Country::DB_File::Builder before you can lookup
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: country codes.
perl-IP-Country-DB_File:
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: This module tries to be API compatible with the other IP::Country
perl-IP-Country-DB_File: modules. The installation of IP::Country is not required.
